column5: I'm heading to Great Wolf Lodge tomorrow morning for work .... I'll be supporting two clients " Community Living"  If ya have time to hook up for a bit Wednesday or Thursday evening or day ... P.M  me a contact # and I'll get in touch.  Photo Opportunity.   Randy   sorry no OFC hat to give away this time.... That's unless T.J can get me one before 9:00  tomorrow mornin'
Are you bringing your speedo?  We had a great time with our boys at GWL this year.
Bring a hat down, i have something for you!
that somehow creates a gnarly image in my mind

My wife, kids' and I were there a few weekends ago and had a good time too. In your travels are you going to pass through the "city"?  If you get anywhere near Bay and Richmond in the day drop me a line as my office is there.

PM'd my cell #.  Funny enough on the drive up to Killarney I saw the turnoff for Sturgeon Falls and was like man I shoulda given Randy a call.... but now that I look at the map that would of been quite the detour!!
